Dark patches on face from hormonal changes

| Treatment | Notes |
|-----------|-------|
| Sunscreen (SPF 30+) | Essential—sun makes it worse |
| Vitamin C | Brightening, safe |
| Tranexamic acid | Effective, check with doctor |
